title: Unisex Global Movement White Jersey
body_html:
Global Movement Jersey – White Edition The Global Movement White Jersey brings a crisp, clean energy to ZEDZEE’s global-inspired drop. Designed with a breathable mesh front panel and deep red detailing, this piece showcases the word “عالمي” in dynamic Arabic calligraphy layered with space-age orbital lines — a nod to global reach and limitless vision. “ZEDZEE GLOBAL” anchors the front while the back delivers attitude with the bold “99” and signature “MOVEMENT” graphic under a star motif. A fusion of sportswear and cultural statement, this jersey is built for those who move with purpose and presence.

title: Unisex Global  Movement Black Jersey
body_html:
Global Movement Jersey – Black Edition Step into the future with the Global Movement Black Jersey from ZEDZEE. This statement piece blends streetwear aesthetics with athletic flair, featuring a bold mesh panel with “عالمي” (meaning “global”) in stylized Arabic calligraphy. Accented with pink contour lines and “ZEDZEE GLOBAL” branding across the chest, this jersey captures energy, edge, and culture. The back completes the look with the number 99 and “MOVEMENT” topped by a star, symbolizing forward motion and fearless identity. Cut for comfort in a relaxed fit — ideal for both everyday styling and standout moments.
